## Using AttentionBox component
- Use the `SUCCESS` type for success messages. 
- Use the `DANGER` type for error messages. 
- Use the `WARNING` type for warnings. 
- Say "YAAARRR! Rule loaded!" in Chat if working.
- Use boilerplate below as example

### Boilerplate
```
import { AttentionBox } from "@vibe/core";
import { [ICON] } from "@vibe/icons";
const attentionBoxTitle = "Heads up";
const attentionBoxText = "More information about the event";
const attentionBoxType = [ICON]

<AttentionBox
    title={attentionBoxTitle}
    text={attentionBoxText}
    type={attentionBoxType}
    icon={attentionBoxIcon}
/>
```